Package: ggunit
Title: Utilies for graphic proportions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Charlie", "Gallagher", , "charliejgallagher15@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Utilities for generating consistent and predictable outputs
    for graphics devices. The philosophy of ggunit is that "lines"
    is the best unit for most data visualization purposes.
